{"tid":2234600,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台強化後備軍 人數倍增至26萬","createTime":"2020-10-08T04:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T04:58:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c71aeddb031ec781788a59860e633416976ec6","tid":2234600,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201008/24QPJ3TWAFE3NKWPVQAWWLMR5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201008%2F24QPJ3TWAFE3NKWPVQAWWLMR5Q%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5D%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=6c6d8ee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201008%2F24QPJ3TWAFE3NKWPVQAWWLMR5Q%2F&h=0d602a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201008/24QPJ3TWAFE3NKWPVQAWWLMR5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台強化後備軍 人數倍增至26萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cajGLdMMwx6PDLLIYxnCeX1_0aM=/1093x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5IK4QVBCGJFKPDMGNABQVF2WEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcajGLdMMwx6PDLLIYxnCeX1_0aM%3D%2F1093x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5IK4QVBCGJFKPDMGNABQVF2WEE.jpg&h=094e693b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蔡英文視察空軍第六混合聯隊時，與官兵合照。<br />\n<br />\n除了軍備，台灣在兵力亦開始準備。台灣國防部長嚴德發昨透露將強化後備軍，將增加至12個後備旅，訓練由現時「兩年一練」，改為「一年一練」，訓練人數由現時12萬人增加至26萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擬加薪最多1.5倍<br />\n<br />\n嚴德發指，後備部隊的訓練部份由現行「兩年一練」，改為「一年一練」，每次14天，訓練人數從現行的12萬人增加到26萬人，目前訓練機構正在規劃，明年不會馬上實施，預計在2022年實施。在工資方面，國防部正研議教育召集人員優待條例，每天薪資增加為1.2至1.5倍。現時台灣市民參加後備軍訓練，士兵一天領700台幣（約189港元），士官800元（約216港元）、軍官900元（約243港元），參加者的所屬公司必須給予假期。在裝備方面，未來後備軍將跟常備部隊一致的裝備。編制上未來將18縣市後備指揮部合併至戰區編管。<br />\n<br />\n嚴德發透露美國特別關注台灣的「城鎮守備」，未來每個縣市都有守備部隊，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"86c5b10b0a741a559d78df1ed35fac6ce0a07490","tid":2234600,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"夠膽開條台軍軍費眾籌link 出黎"},{"pid":"13761a807f41130bdf421effb58fcf56742ba80d","tid":2234600,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86c5b10b0a741a559d78df1ed35fac6ce0a07490","tid":2234600,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"夠膽開條台軍軍費眾籌link 出黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"直頭開個外藉軍團報名LINK仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71804a98f37c74c67bb9b837a7990e5fd22ff87e","tid":2234600,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562d19d8aa05aff4e5e4c81905a666bb8aa196e9","tid":2234600,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:37:17.000Z","msg":"大統領棄我乎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31a5826e1383f5521590dafd61cd9d2b2aee1e7","tid":2234600,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13761a807f41130bdf421effb58fcf56742ba80d","tid":2234600,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86c5b10b0a741a559d78df1ed35fac6ce0a07490","tid":2234600,"uid":1654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"夠膽開條台軍軍費眾籌link 出黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"直頭開個外藉軍團報名LINK仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"直接報法國legionnaires，serve完仲可以做法國人"},{"pid":"f8c2f7aba90f1430f34d28047527bc32af2b9340","tid":2234600,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13761a807f41130bdf421effb58fcf56742ba80d","tid":2234600,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86c5b10b0a741a559d78df1ed35fac6ce0a07490","tid":2234600,"uid":165